## Category Definitions
- analysis_export: Generated reverse-engineering artifacts (pattern scans, coverage reports)

- sdk_example: PSYQ example projects for pattern comparison / library call usage
- raw_asset: Supplemental assets or demos outside primary game data
- misc: Files not falling cleanly into other categories
